<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <%- include('../fragments/head.ejs') %>
        <title>Guns of the Patriot</title>
</head>

<body>
    <%- include('../fragments/header.ejs') %>

        <main style="padding: 50px; text-align: center; color: var(--text-main);">
            <section class="about-section">
                <h1 style="color: var(--accent-primary); font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;">OUR MISSION</h1>
                <hr style="border-color: var(--accent-primary); width: 50%; margin: 20px auto;">

                <article
                    style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; text-align: left; font-size: 1.2rem; line-height: 1.6;">
                    <p>
                        Founded in the crucible of modern conflict, <strong>Guns of the Patriot (GotP)</strong> emerged
                        as
                        the premier logistics and supply network for private military contractors and independent
                        tactical
                        operatives worldwide.
                    </p>
                    <br>
                    <p>
                        What started as a small underground distribution hub has evolved into a global titan of
                        commerce. We don't just sell assets; we provide reliability when it matters most. Our catalogue
                        is strictly curated, ensuring that every piece of hardware meets the highest combat-ready
                        standards.
                    </p>
                    <br>
                    <p>
                        <em>"Peace is a fragile machine. We provide the spare parts."</em>
                    </p>
                </article>

                <br><br>
                <img src="/resources/images/Patriot.png" alt="GotP Logo"
                    style="max-width: 300px; border-radius: 10px;">
            </section>
        </main>

        <!-- <%- include('../fragments/footer.ejs') %> -->
</body>

</html>